# Copy to .env and set values. Used by the server and by Vite in dev for POST /api/register.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# GoHighLevel (GHL) — choose one method
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Option A: Inbound Webhook (recommended for automation)
# 1. In GHL subaccount: Workflows → New → Trigger: "Inbound Webhook"
# 2. Copy the webhook URL and paste below
# 3. In the workflow: add "Create/Update Contact", map firstName + email from the trigger
# 4. Add any automation (emails, tags, etc.)
# GHL_WEBHOOK_URL=https://services.leadconnectorhq.com/hooks/...

# Option B: Contacts API (creates contact directly; use "Contact Created" workflow trigger)
# 1. In GHL: Settings → API Keys → create key with contacts.write for your subaccount
# 2. Get your Location (subaccount) ID from the GHL URL or Settings
# GHL_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
# GHL_LOCATION_ID=your_location_id_here

# Optional: port for production server
# PORT=3000
